h distance from the core but move at less than the jet speed.\nThe trailing components exhibit motion and structure consistent with the\ntriggering of pinch modes by the superluminal component.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Jan 2001 15:50:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-06"}
